entry.def: If something is unclear, it is not known or not certain.

example.ex: It is unclear how much popular support they have among the island's population...
example.tran: 目前还不清楚他们在岛上的民众中间有多高的支持率。

example.ex: Just what the soldier was doing in Bireij is unclear...
example.tran: 就连那个士兵在比雷杰干什么都不清楚。

entry.tran: 不明白的；不清楚的；不确定的
entry.def: If you are unclear about something, you do not understand it properly or are not sure about it.

example.ex: He is still unclear about his own future...
example.tran: 他仍然不清楚自己的将来会怎样。

example.ex: Experts remain unclear as to why the danger appears to have been steadily increasing.
example.tran: 专家依然不清楚为什么危险似乎一直在增大。
